Package com.lambdaschool.schools.services

Contains the services that are used to retrieve and manipulate data in the application. Contains the contract stating what each client can do with the data in the application. The majority of the work of the application resides in this package.
  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    CoursesService
    The Service that works with the Course Model
    StudentService
    The service that works with the Student Model
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CoursesServiceImpl
    Implements the CoursesService
    StudentServiceImpl
    Implements the StudentService Interface
